Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それは高鳴った交響曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:42.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想いと願い一つにする…炎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}震えるHEART BEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}愚かな愛の情熱を
